(6,'Norton 360 5.0',29.99,0.6,4,'2012-10-01',100,1,'Norton 360 delivers comprehensive, easy-to-use protection that defends you, your computer, and your files from just about any online threat. PC Tune-up fine-tunes your computer so it runs its best. Automatic backup keeps your digital photos and other important files safe from loss. And exclusive Insight technology blocks emerging viruses and keeps you safe from cybercriminals when you go online.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\"><b>Languages</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Instruction Manual Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>English/French</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_HypName\">Operating Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>English/French</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>30 Day(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10163036</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">You can never have  too much protection. That\'s why Norton 360 provides comprehensive,  easy-to-use protection that defends your identity, your computer, and  your important files against nearly any threat. It delivers fast, light  protection in an incredibly easy-to-use, all-in-one solution that does  more to keep you safe.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFew things are more frustrating than when  your computer slows down. So Norton 360 includes PC Tuneup which  automatically fine-tunes key computer settings, frees up memory, and  removes unnecessary files to help keep your PC running its best.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNorton  360 also includes automated online or local backup to help keep them  safe from loss. And, it couldn\'t be easier &ndash; simply set it and forget  it. And if disaster should strike, you can instantly restore your files  with a few simple clicks.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNorton 360 protects you when you go  online by warning you of unsafe websites in your search results and  automatically remembering and entering your usernames and passwords. So  you can search, socialize, shop, and bank online without worrying about  getting ripped off. It even lets you check your Facebook Wall and News  Feed for bad links right from within Norton 360.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNorton 360 also  features exclusive Insight technology. It\'s proven to block emerging  viruses so you can email, chat, and download files with industry-leading  protection from just about any threat. It even updates your protection  every 5-15 minutes to keep you a step ahead of new threats.</p>',4,13,1),
(7,'Microsoft Office Home and Business 2010 - English',359.99,1.99,4,'2012-10-01',1000,1,'Microsoft Office Home and Business 2010 is the essential software suite for managing small businesses and working from home. Enhanced tools and features help you run your business, connect with customers, and organize your household more efficiently.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\"><b>Languages</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Instruction Manual Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Info Not Available</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_HypName\">Operating Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>English</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>30 Day(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10145421</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Due to  the legal restrictions of the Quebec French Language Charter, this  product cannot be delivered in Quebec. We apologize for any  inconvenience.</b><br />\r\n<br />\r\nOffice Home and Business 2010 features new  photo, video, and text effects for creating standout documents and  presentations. New communication tools in Outlook 2010 help you stay in  touch and organized. Office Home and Business 2010 makes it easier than  ever for you to manage things in the office, at home, or in between.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Create reports and presentations that command attention</li>\r\n    <li>Clarify your financial picture fast with analysis tools, charts, and color formatting that help you cut through the data clutter</li>\r\n    <li>Create professional-looking charts with ease - format axes, titles, and other chart labels with a few clicks</li>\r\n    <li>Transform  any presentation from simple to sophisticated with easy photo- and  video-editing tools, text effects, and dramatic slide transitions</li>\r\n    <li>Set up your e-mail fast and communicate right away with tools that keep contacts and messages well organized</li>\r\n    <li>Manage projects - combine your notes, media, documents, and other materials into a digital notebook</li>\r\n    <li>Easily store files and documents online using advanced security features so you never lose them</li>\r\n    <li>Access, view, and edit your documents from home, the office, or any PC that\'s connected to the Internet</li>\r\n    <li>Collaborate with others - invite them to see online files so they can review and edit work</li>\r\n</ul>',4,2,1),
(8,'Kaspersky Internet Security 2012 - 3 User',19.99,1.99,4,'2012-10-01',100,1,'A hybrid approach to digital security. Our innovative Hybrid Protection combines the power of the cloud with our advanced technologies - housed on your PC - to deliver a faster, more effective response to today\'s complex, ever-evolving threats.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\"><b>Languages</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Instruction Manual Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>English/French</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_HypName\">Operating Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>English/French</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>30 Day(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10178437</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">You\'ll benefit  from the speed and immense volume of the security data of the cloud,  while also benefiting from our ability to: detect and analyze suspicious  behaviour on your PC; capture malware that is passed to you while  you\'re offline via a USB or other device; and block, treat, or rollback  harmful activity. The result of this hybrid combination: unmatched  security that won\'t slow you down.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Rapid,  Real-Time Reaction to New Threats: New Internet threats emerge with  lightning speed, and the latest Kaspersky technologies are there to  protect you with real-time data from the cloud. Plus, you\'re linked to  the Kaspersky Security Network, which leverages threat data gathered  from millions of participating users\' systems around the world.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Secure  Online Banking and Shopping: Kaspersky delivers a safer online  experience with multiple layers of protection to keep your financial  information secure as you bank and shop online.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Innovative  Technologies, Including Our Unique Online: Banking mode and URL Advisor,  secure your credit card numbers and transaction details, and alert you  in real-time to potential phishing attacks and malicious websites.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Advanced  Identity Theft Protection: Your digital identity is safe from even the  sneakiest online fraud with the latest cloud-based and proactive  anti-phishing technologies. Plus, our unique, on-screen Virtual Keyboard  allows you to use mouse-clicks to enter your credit card numbers and  bank information, so they can\'t be tracked or stolen by keyloggers,  hackers, or identity thieves.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Secure Social Networking: The  latest Kaspersky technologies allow you to fully enjoy social  networking, knowing your Facebook, MySpace, and Twitter accounts won\'t  receive malicious links or software from your friends. Plus, you can  ensure your children\'s safety by controlling which contacts are allowed  for communication, monitoring messaging logs, and specifying any  personal information you want blocked from transmitting.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Instant  Security Checks: The security status and reputation of files and  websites is now at your fingertips. With a single mouse-click, File  Advisor uses cloud-based technologies to check the safety of any file  you\'d like to access. And, our updated URL Advisor adds colour-coded  tags to all web links within search results to advise you of the danger  level of the link and subsequent pages. Search the web with confidence  that you won\'t stumble onto any dangerous websites.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Advanced  Parental Controls: Keep your kids safe and responsible with Kaspersky\'s  family protection. Control access to the PC, Internet, applications,  games, and websites. Block, limit, or log communications via IM and  social networks. Control file downloads. Even block the transfer of  private data such as phone and credit card numbers. Now you can easily  and conveniently protect your kids online even when you\'re not right  there.</li>\r\n</ul>',4,2,1),
