tl56_LN\">Thunderbolt Ports</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>No</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl57_LN\">Other Inputs/Outputs</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>No</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl58_LN\"><b>Power</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl59_LN\">Approximate In-use Battery Life</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Up To 10 Hours</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl60_LN\">Approximate Standby Battery Life</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Information Not Available</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl61_LN\">Battery - Number of Cells</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Information Not Available</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl62_LN\">Battery - Capacity</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>5300 mAh</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl63_LN\">Charge over USB</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Yes</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl64_LN\"><b>Physical Features</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl65_LN\">Sensors</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Ambient Light Sensor; Accelerometer; Gyroscope</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl66_LN\">Hard-key QWERTY Keyboard</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>No</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl67_LN\">Colour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Black</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl68_LN\">Height</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>13 cm</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl69_LN\">Depth</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>0.97 cm</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl70_LN\">Width</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>19.4 cm</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl71_LN\">Weight</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>425 g</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl72_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl73_LN\">Warranty Parts</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl74_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>10166449</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">Less than  half-an-inch thin and weighing under a pound, BlackBerry\'s PlayBook puts  remarkable portability in a single powerful device that boasts a sleek,  slim profile. Everything appears on the 7-inch LCD multi-touch  capacitive screen, so you can swipe, select and scroll with a mere  gesture of the hand. And it\'s not just about looks - the PlayBook houses  a 1GHz dual core processor alongside 1GB RAM to give you full computing  power in tablet format. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe user-friendly BlackBerry Tablet OS  with support for symmetric multiprocessing makes everything easy to use.  Easily type messages on the on-screen keyboard and get more done in  less time with true multitasking. And with apps in constant development,  there\'s no shortage in extended functionality. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe internet is  about freedom and unrestricted access to information. The BlackBerry  PlayBook was designed to let you experience that the way it was meant to  be - with full support for Flash, HTML 5, and everything else a web  without borders offers.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nVideo conferencing and shooting  capabilities are second to none. With two HD cameras - one front-facing  (3MP) and another on the back (5MP) - you can chat face to face with  family, friends, coworkers and clients as well as shoot amazingly crisp  video and images from the rear camera. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe PlayBook covers all  the bases. It has micro-USB and micro-HDMI connectivity, 802.11a/b/g/n  WiFi, Bluetooth 2.1+EDR, push technology and more. And of course, it\'s  enterprise-ready. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease note: This product is pre-loaded with  English only operating system. French operating system will be available  for download in May 2011.</p>',1,1,5),
(13,'Logitech Harmony One Universal Remote Control ',14.99,3,5,'2011-10-01',100,1,'With control of up to 15 devices and one-touch activity controls, this is the only remote you may ever need. Say good-bye to cheat sheets. Everyone in the family can select what they want to do, such as \"Watch TV,\" your Harmony remote does the rest.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_LN\">Warranty Parts</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10180321</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">FEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Replaces  up to 15 remotes: You can control your home-entertainment devices with  one remote, reducing clutter and complexity in your living room</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Full-colour touch screen: You\'ll enjoy easy, one-touch access to any entertainment activity</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Sculpted, backlit buttons: Backlit buttons in logical zones allow you to find the right channel, even in the dark.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Ergonomic design: The remote fits comfortably in your hand, making it easier to use.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Rechargeable: Your remote recharges in its base station so you won\'t be looking for batteries when you want to be watching TV.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Guided  online setup: You connect your Harmony remote to your computer and  you\'re guided through every step. If you hit a snag, customer support is  ready to help.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Works with 225,000+ devices: Support for  5000+ brands and 225,000+ devices, so you know it will work with what  you have today and what you\'ll add tomorrow.</li>\r\n</ul>',7,9,2),
(14,'Samsung Rechargeable Adult 3D Glasses',99.99,0,4,'2011-10-01',100,1,' Long gone are the days of less-than-flattering paper 3D glasses. Sleek and stylish, these Samsung 3D glasses are both fashion and function. Designed for use with your Samsung 3D HDTV and 3D components, they\'re the shades you\'ll want to wear. *Please Note: Only compatible with Samsung C Series TVs.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_LN\">Warranty Parts</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10140322</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">Samsung 3D Active  glasses let you enjoy a truly realistic 3D viewing experience and  contain a built-in emitter. The lenses alternately darken in perfect  synchronization with the TV\'s refresh rate to generate a lifelike 3D  image that is free from ghosting and visual distortion. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Supports 3D Full HD 1080p image resolution</li>\r\n    <li>Designed for adult use</li>\r\n    <li>Lightweight design</li>\r\n    <li>Built-in emitter</li>\r\n    <li>Rechargeable</li>\r\n</ul>',7,8,1),
(15,'HP 15.6\" Intel Pentium B950',34.99,0.99,5,'2011-10-01',100,1,' The HP G6-1c39 laptop gets you online, keeps you productive, and comes complete with great entertainment capabilities. It\'s powered by an Intel Pentium B950 processor and 4GB RAM, while a bright and crisp 15.6-inch LED backlit display ensures awesome high definition viewing. Other great features include HDMI connectivity, built-in WiFi, a 500GB hard drive, and over 5 hours of power on a single charge.','<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">FEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>An Intel Pentium B950 processor and 4GB system memory offer up plenty of horse power with efficient performance</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Store your media on the large 500GB hard drive</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Watch  movies, work more efficiently, and see everything with total clarity  thanks to the 15.6-inch LED-backlit HD display and integrated Intel HD  graphics</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Burn your own DVDs with the SuperMulti DVD Burner</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Connect, face to face, with family and friends with the built-in webcam and mic</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>An HDMI output lets you easily connect to your HDTV and work, play, surf on the big screen</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>802.11b/g/n wireless connectivity offers optimal wireless performance in your home network and public hotspots</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Built-in memory card reader</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Get up to 5.5 hours of power on a single charge</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>This model comes complete with Windows 7 Home Premium</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Please  Note: This product contains both English and French operating  instructions and system software. In this context GB or Gigabytes refers  to 1 Billion Bytes. The actual formatted capacity will be less.</p>',2,1,4),
