p>1 x 6.5&quot; Mid/Woofer</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">This system was  designed for minimalist appearance in your space, while delivering  maximum sound quality. High tech materials and features, such as  Satellite PowerPorts and Subwoofer Slot Load venting technologies,  ensure superior system performance, delivering rich, full-bodied, big  speaker sound from stylish, compact packages.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Satellites  feature a 3-1/4 inch (8.25cm) mineral-filled polymer dynamic balance  midrange driver for clear, distortion-free midrange</li>\r\n    <li>Center speaker uses two midrange drivers to handle the centre channel\'s high output requirements with minimal distortion</li>\r\n    <li>The broad dispersion design allows everyone in the listening area to hear clear, well-balanced sound</li>\r\n    <li>Connect your RM Series Satellites securely and conveniently with their high quality 5-way binding post inputs</li>\r\n    <li>Powered subwoofer with 10 inch driver and Slot Load Bass Vent pours out deep, efficient bass</li>\r\n    <li>Satellites  are magnetically shielded for safe placement near your state-of-the-art  TV or video monitor with no risk of video distortion</li>\r\n</ul>',6,13,1),
(20,'Polk Audio 5.1 Home Theatre Speaker System (RM6750)',399.99,0.99,4,'2012-10-10',100,1,'The Polk Audio RM6750 is a complete home theatre audio solution for people who crave true cinema excitement without breaking the bank. The integrated Power Port Bass Vent designed right onto the back of the compact satellite and center channel speakers. It\'s the same technology used in full-sized Polk Audio speakers-improves lower midrange response and all-important sub/sat blending.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_HypName\"># of Speakers Included</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>6</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">2-Way Speakers</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Yes</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_HypName\">Center Speakers Power</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>100 Watts</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_HypName\">Center Speakers Size</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>28.42(W) x 10.95(H) x 14.76(D) cm</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_LN\">Colour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Black</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl06_HypName\">Crossover Point</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Not Applicable</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl07_LN\">Finish</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Black</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>   