(21,'Panasonic 14.1 MP Digital Camera (DMC-FZ40K)',269.99,100,4,'2011-10-01',100,1,'The Panasonic DMCFZ40K features Panasonic\'s Intelligent Auto Mode that automatically activates a host of advanced functions and technologies that make it easy to capture beautiful, clear motion images, including Face Recognition. When a familiar face appears in the frame, the camera will prioritize focus and exposure to capture it beautifully.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\"><b>Image Sensor</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Sensor Type</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>1/2.33 Inch Type CCD</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_HypName\">Sensor Size</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>6.13 mm x 4.6 mm</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_HypName\">Total Pixels</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>14.5 MP</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_HypName\">Effective Pixels</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>14.1 MP</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl06_HypName\">Image Processor</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Venus IV</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl07_LN\"><b>Lens</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl0