(26,'XBOX 360 250GB Halo Reach & Fable III Console Bundle',299.99,0,4,'2011-10-01',100,1,'The new XBOX 360 has everything you love about XBOX 360 with a few improvements that include a massive 250GB hard drive, built-in 802.11n WiFi connectivity, a cool black colour and whisper-quiet operation. This bundle includes Fable III and Halo Reach games (download onl','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_LN\">Warranty Parts</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10182217</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">The XBOX 360 was  the first console to offer gaming in Full HD 1080p, with a library of  games unrivaled in size. It\'s since had a makeover in the form of the  XBOX 360, which is still home to the most robust HD gaming experience  out there, but is now a fraction of the size of its predecessor. It\'s  also equipped with an integrated 250GB hard drive, the latest 802.11n  wireless connectivity, and construction and components that allow for  remarkably quiet operation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis bundle includes two games: Fable III and Halo: Reach (download only)</p>',11,13,1),
(27,'Madden NFL 12 (XBOX 360)',59.99,0,4,'2012-10-01',100,1,'Get closer than ever to the NFL in Madden NFL 12. An all-new collision system, advanced defense AI enhancements, and custom playbooks bring NFL Sundays into your home like never before. You make the calls, you make the plays, and you control it all as you lead your team to Super Bowl victory.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\">Instruction Manual Language</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>English/French</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Operating Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>English</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>30 Day(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>10172079</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">FEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>The  collision system gives you full control of players up to the point of  impact, so you can tackle and block with the most authentic precision to  date.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>The collision system uses your player\'s momentum  along with more than 100 new tackles, including 40 gang tackles, for the  greatest impact.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Advanced defensive AI offer over 100 enhancements for the smartest defense ever.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Players  in zone and man coverage will recognize and react to plays, which means  they can even break out of assignments when appropriate so you get a  defensive team that works together.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Custom playbooks give  you the freedom to create the ultimate game plan by modifying an  existing playbook or building your own using up to 400 offensive or  defensive plays from 75 playbooks.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Integrate your custom  playbook into your game plan and use it with the improved GameFlow  system, which executes an authentic, situational game plan for you.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Enjoy  team-specific run-outs featuring mascots and cheerleaders, authentic  broadcast cameras, lifelike 3D grass, and dynamic time-of-day.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Franchise  mode includes more than 100 new features and enhancements, including  expanded rosters, an all-new rookie scouting system, a free-agent  bidding system, and more.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>In Superstar mode, you can now  control the growth of your superstar with an all-new progression system  that allows you to earn skill points by participating in practice and  games.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Dynamic Player Performance creates unprecedented  realism as a player\'s skills and confidence rise and fall based on his  performance throughout a game.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>The perfect combination of  Madden NFL Football, fantasy football, and trading cards comes to life  with Madden Ultimate Team; earn, buy, auction, and trade players as you  build your ultimate team of NFL stars and legends.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Create an online community and play head-to-head against up to 2,000 friends.</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Enjoy exclusive access to all of your NFL.com fantasy teams inside of Madden NFL 12 (available after first title update).</li>\r\n</ul>',11,1,1),
(28,'PlayStation3 320GB Uncharted 3 Bundle',299.99,0,4,'2012-10-10',100,1,'With the PlayStation3 320GB system, you get free PlayStation Network membership, built-in Wi-Fi, and 320GB of hard disk drive storage for games, music, videos and photos. And every PS3 system comes with a built-in Blu-ray player to give you pristine picture quality and the best high-definition viewing experience available. Plus, this fall bundle comes with Uncharted 3.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_LN\">Warranty Parts</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10181734</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">Whether it\'s gaming, Blu-ray movies, music or online services, experience it all with the PlayStation3 system.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Bigger 320GB hard drive for all your digital downloads</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Connect to your HDTV via a single HDMI cable</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Built-in WiFi means easy connectivity with your home network, the internet, and the PlayStation Network</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Download exclusive games, movies and TV shows from the PlayStation Network</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Save your CD catalogue onto your hard drive and create a playlist library</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Upload  personal photos from a portable memory device and view them in one of  five slideshow modes for hours of enjoyment with friends and family</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Connect  your digital video camera directly to your PS3 system or save your  videos directly onto your hard drive for easier management and viewing</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Features  CD/DVD/DivX playback, BD Live, an integrated internet browser, video  chat, parental controls, Bluetooth, the DUALSHOCK 3 wireless controller,  and more</li>\r\n    <br />\r\n    <li>Includes Uncharted 3 game</li>\r\n</ul>',12,13,3),
(29,'Call Of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 (PC)',59.99,0,4,'2012-10-10',100,1,'Call of Duty: Modern Warfare is back with another intensed action-packed gameplay. Experience gripping and heart-racing action as you face off against a new threat dedicated to bringing the world the brink of collapse. MW3 promises to be an intense and gripping saga of heroic proportions.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\"><b>Languages</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Operating Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>English</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">Instruction Manual Language</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>English/French</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>30 Day(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10170837</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">*** System Requirements is currently not available ***</p>',13,13,1),
(30,'World Of Warcraft: Cataclysm (PC)',19.99,0,4,'2012-10-10',100,1,'  An ancient evil lies dormant within Deepholm, the domain of earth in the Elemental Plane. Hidden away in a secluded sanctuary, the corrupted Dragon Aspect Deathwing has waited, recovering from the wounds of his last battle against Azeroth and biding his time until he can reforge the world in molten fire. ','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\"><b>Languages</b></span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n    <br />\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Operating Language</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Information Not Available</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">Instruction Manual Language</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Information Not Available</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>30 Day(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>10130937</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p>Soon, Deathwing  the Destroyer will return to Azeroth, and his eruption from Deepholm  will sunder the world, leaving a festering wound across the continents.  As the Horde and Alliance race to the epicenter of the cataclysm, the  kingdoms of Azeroth will witness seismic shifts in power, the kindling  of a war of the elements, and the emergence of unlikely heroes who will  rise up to protect their scarred and broken world 