(37,'Itec iPod Touch 4 Protection Kit (T382)',29.99,0.01,4,'2012-10-01',100,1,'The iPod Touch 4th Generation Protection Kit includes 3 different cases for your iPod Touch: clear acrylic case, silicone case, and sports band case with adjustable arm band. *Please Note: iPod Not Included.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>10156361</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">The clear acrylic  case snaps onto your iPod Touch for protection. The one piece black  armor case is perfect for on-the-go protection. The sports band case  features a reflective face for security while jogging at night and an  adjustable band with extra-soft and absorbent material and adjustable  hook and loop closure system.</p>',18,3,3),
(38,'Apple Composite AV Cable (MC748ZM/A)',46.99,0.01,4,'2012-10-10',100,1,'Easily connect your iPod, iPhone, or iPad to the composite video inputs on a TV. The cable also features audio and USB connectors.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>10162829</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">Connect an iPod,  iPhone or iPad to your television with the Apple Composite AV Cable,  gather up your friends and watch videos or slideshows together on the  big screen. You can also connect this composite AV cable to your stereo  or powered speakers for a room-filling audio experience.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe  Composite AV Cable connects to your device or Universal Dock via the  30-pin dock connector and to your TV, home cinema receiver or stereo  receiver via the composite video and red/white analog audio ports. The  cable also features a USB connector that you can plug in to a power  source.</p>',18,3,1),(39,'Monster Diddybeats iPod/iPhone Control In-Ear Headphones with Built-in Mic ',79.99,0.99,4,'2012-10-10',100,1,'Design meets fashion meets Monster sound. Diddybeats combine the outstanding sound of Monster headphones with the subtle, unique style of Diddy. They feature a speaker design that better captures and reproduces the nuances of today\'s hottest music, and come complete with a carrying case.','<dl class=\"std-list features\">\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\">                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl01_HypName\">Cord Length</a></dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1.22 m</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt>                     <a id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl02_HypName\">Folding</a></dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Yes</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl03_LN\">Magnet Type</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>Neodymium</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl04_LN\">Plug</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>Gold</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl05_LN\">Warranty Labour</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl06_LN\">Warranty Parts</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>1 Year(s)</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt class=\"alt\"><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl07_LN\">Water/Sweat Resistant</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd class=\"alt\">\r\n    <p>No</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n    <dt><span id=\"ctl00_CC_ctl00_UT_RB_ctl00_TC_Tab_FeatureSpecs_repProductSpecs_ctl08_LN\">WebID</span>                     </dt>\r\n    <dd>\r\n    <p>10144893</p>\r\n    </dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h3 class=\"text\">More information</h3>\r\n<p class=\"text\">FEATURES:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>ControlTalk gives you on-cable iPod/iPhone playback control and hands-free calling for iPhone and many music phones</li>\r\n    <li>Integrates aluminum and high gloss enamel into a new, sophisticated shape that pushes the Class Meter to &quot;HIGH&quot;</li>\r\n    <li>Accurate speaker design delivers the details of today\'s hottest music with extreme clarity and deep bass</li>\r\n    <li>Includes multiple sizes of single and triple layer sound isolating ear tips for replacement and comfort</li>\r\n    <